      • ClimateLogicChooser

        public ClimateLogicChooser()
        Overloaded constructor for Climate Logic Chooser. Set up to initiate an origin process, this creates passes to default constructor a new JDialog, title = origin process, false for modality, null items, null choosen items, time step count to 1 and time step num to 1 meaning initial.

      • initialize

        private void initialize()
        Initializes Climate logic chooser dialog, by setting check boxes depending on items entered in constructor, sets layout, and adds to panel. Sets the time text field to the sum of time steps, and number time text to the num time step.

      • this_windowClosing

        public void this_windowClosing(java.awt.event.WindowEvent e)
        If window closing X event occurs, clears out the chosen items, adds selected items to chosen item array. Gets the time step count from text field, gets the number of time step from text field, sets the dialog to not visible and disposes.
